      "shortest": true,
      "solution": "s = input().split()\n\nfor i in range(1,len(s)):\n    while s[i][0].lower() == s[i-1][-1].lower():\n        s[i] = s[i][1:]\n        if not len(s[i]):\n            s.insert(0, s.pop(i))\n            break\n\nprint(''.join(s))\n",
